      • EXECUTOR_ABORT_ON_CORRUPTION

        public static final String EXECUTOR_ABORT_ON_CORRUPTION
        Procedure replay sanity check. In case a WAL is missing or unreadable we may lose information about pending/running procedures. Set this to true in case you want the Master failing on load if a corrupted procedure is encountred. (Default is off, because we prefer having the Master up and running and fix the "in transition" state "by hand")
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值
